messages.content: Oh thank you Anne very much :) this are really nice wishes and it's nice to see you all remembering me ;) I wish you and your family a lovely christmas time, too and enjoy this one... Have you see my message before ?? I hope you have ... Say nice greetings to torin and Eden. you must know how nice they are *-* and nice greetings to pete you have a lovely family ;) thank you very much yours Tanja <3
Merry Christmas Tanya :) We hope you and your family have a lovely time. Best Wishes Anne, Pete, Torin and Eden x

Heei ;) how are YOU?? What are you doing? Did you have a nice trip Top wales ?? ;) the weather in germany is horrible and it's cold :o often we are talking about our nice time in england ... I will never forget these time ;) how are the kids ?? ;) i tried to text you earlier but I forgot it every time ... :( I'm sorry about this.. Lovely greatings from Ulm... <3 and thank you for everything.. You have a nice family ! I hope you will answer me :* Tanja ( sorry for my gramatical und writing mistakes)
